form([formgroup]='coverTypesForm')
  .form-group
    label(for='code') Code
    input#code.form-control(type='text', placeholder='', formcontrolname='code')
    .alert.alert-danger.mt-3(*ngif="coverTypesForm.get('code').invalid && (coverTypesForm.get('code').dirty || coverTypesForm.get('code').touched)")
      div(*ngif="coverTypesForm.get('code').errors.required")
        | Code is required.
      div(*ngif="coverTypesForm.get('code').errors.maxlength")
        | Code cannot be more than 50 characters long.
      div(*ngif="coverTypesForm.get('code').errors.exists")
        | Code should be unique.
  .form-group
    label(for='description')
      | Description 
      span.text-secondary  (Optional)
    textarea#description.form-control(placeholder='', rows='3', formcontrolname='description')
    .alert.alert-danger.mt-3(*ngif="coverTypesForm.get('description').invalid && (coverTypesForm.get('description').dirty || coverTypesForm.get('description').touched)")
      div(*ngif="coverTypesForm.get('description').errors.maxlength")
        | Description cannot be more than 250 characters long.
